buyerAgent.name: The William Elias Home Selling Team

data.description: Welcome to your new home – a delightful 3-bdrm ranch with beautiful updates throughout. This all-brick home features timeless appeal with aluminum trim accents and vinyl windows. Step inside to a refreshed interior adorned with all-new vinyl plank floors in the spacious living room and kitchen. The dream kitchen includes white cabinets, a ceramic tile backsplash, and all stainless steel appliances, purchased brand new in 2020. The full bath has been thoughtfully updated, featuring new ceramic tile plank floors, a stylish vanity and mirror, and a ceramic-tiled shower. Venture outdoors to enjoy the expansive 20x20 ft. deck, providing an ideal space for entertaining guests or simply unwinding. Experience the joy of homeownership in a home that checks all the boxes for comfort, convenience, and quality. Schedule a showing today!
